data.description: Just under 3000 square foot remodeled four bedroom farm house...As you enter the foyer your eyes are drawn to the oversized gas-log fireplace with blower and gorgeous wood mantel. To the left is a well appointed Kitchen with gas stove and Smart Refrigerator that overlooks the living area.  Right of the Foyer you pass by the private office as well as large laundry room leading to the massive Master Suite downstairs with walk in closet, large master bath, freestanding soaker tub and separate shower as well as private access to the covered wraparound 1300 square foot porch!!!  Upstairs findS 3 remodeled good sized bedrooms as well as an additional living area. To the southeast of the home you can't miss the approximately 37x181 barn with existing stalls on one side and storage on the other...the front is a 36x36 insulated workshop with electric and epoxy floor.  Partial Arena as well!!  10 MORE ACRES AVAILABLE FOR 28K
